title: Can't see club I created or tag in game.
body: My IGN is Ells and I created the club penile dysfunction a while ago when clubs came out and haven't been able to see the club in a couple months. Was wondering if some one could help me. Thanks!

replies.body: I mean, it's not the oddest club name I've seen.  Your club may have been out of sync, so I booped it for a refresh.  Just keep in mind that if the community deems your name a bit inappropriate, we may need to change it.  Let me know if that clears things up!
That's completely understandable, and thank you it did work :D!
